title: Nice and quiet Hyde Park Garage Apartment
posting_body: This Hyde Park studio is at a perfect location and is very charming.
It is around the corner from 38th and Duval in Hyde Park (Central Austin).
It is has hardwood floors, stove/oven and refrigerator.
The apartment has many windows and brings in a ton of natural light.
It is on the UT bus line and car parking is within steps of the front door of this apartment!
This is the best location you will find in Hyde Park/ North Campus.
Thanks for looking, email me for a showing.
$1,325 monthly rent, $1,300 security deposit $29 application fee.
Well-qualified applicants, strong credit and documented income, stable employment history, landlord references, no previous evictions, pets/number of pets at landlord discretion.
